extends ../../layout

block style
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/lib/swiper/css/swiper.min.css')
  link(rel='stylesheet/less', href='/css/my.swiper.css')
block content
  include ../../component/navbar.pug
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-3
        include ../component/menu.pug
      .col-md-9
        h2 threshold
        p 拖动的临界点值(单位为px)，如果触摸距离小于该值滑块不会被拖动。
  
        h4 threshold参数
        p 类型：<span class="label label-info">number</span> 默认：<span class="label label-info">false</span> 举例：<span class="label label-info">200</span> 启用版本：<span class="label label-info">3.0.0</span>

        h4 效果演示
        .desc
          p 必须拖动大于200px后slide才会开始移动。
          .swiper-container#e1
            .swiper-wrapper
              .swiper-slide slider1
              .swiper-slide slider2
              .swiper-slide slider3

block script
  script(src="/lib/swiper/js/swiper.jquery.min.js")
  script(src="/js/my.swiper.js")
  script.
    $(function() {
      var e1 = new Swiper('#e1', {
        threshold: 200,
      });
    })
